{"tid":2192168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國企旗下Karma汽車在美被控剽竊","createTime":"2020-09-07T02:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T08:44:37.000Z","uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"462dcdb192cc0fe8e2cf74b1860ecbea9fe3584f","tid":2192168,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cn.epochtimes.com/b5/20/8/6/n12312105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F8%2F6%2Fn12312105.htm&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpyWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=0ea9963a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cn.epochtimes.com/b5/20/8/6/n12312105.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2020年08月07日訊】（大紀元記者張玉潔綜合報導）中國萬向集團旗下Karma電動車公司近日被告上美國加州法庭，該公司被控在與美國同業企業商討合作協議的過程中，欺騙並竊取對方的合資計劃，企圖將此據為己有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8月5日消息，美國VLF Automotive汽車公司今年6月份向加州法院提起訴訟，指控中國萬向集團旗下的Karma汽車公司竊取商業資料。<br />\n<br />\nVLF在訴訟中表示，VLF去年秋季與Karma汽車分享了其「豪華悍馬」（Humvee project）的計劃，希望兩家公司合資向中國市場推出這款汽車，雙方簽署了保密協議。<br />\n<br />\n但是，Karma的首席執行官周亮（Lance Zhou）卻私自聯繫VLF的合作製造廠商，企圖自行生產這款電動車，獨自將這一計劃推向中國市場。<br />\n<br />\nVLF要求Karma賠償至少1850萬美元，以彌補VLF在該計劃投資方面的損失，並彌補其股票預期的獲利。<br />\n<br />\nKarma總部在美國加州，前身是美國豪華電動車公司Fisker Automotive，2013年申請破產。中國萬向集團2014年2月收購了Fisker Automotive，2015年9月將其更名為Karma汽車。<br />\n<br />\n但是，Karma汽車的發展一直不佳，2019年僅售出1000輛電動車，同年年末裁員近150人。<br />\n<br />\n中國萬向集團是一家大型民企，但內部設有中共黨支部，該集團創始人的兒子兼任黨委書記和董事長，曾於2018年和2019年兩次公開宣布成立慈善信託，意味著相關資產交給信託機構後不再屬於家族所有。<br />\n<br />\n而從萬向集團的財報可見，截至2019年上半年末，萬向控股總負債為1040.73億元人民幣，資產負債率為84.69%。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，萬向集團旗下上市公司萬向錢潮的營收同比下滑6.87%，是近20年來的首次下滑；淨利潤同比下滑25.82%。同年，萬向集團旗下最大房地產公司順發恆業的營收同比下滑39.29%，淨利潤同比下滑40.8%。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：孫芸#"},{"pid":"adfc4bac57a1d2731dcc84646b23d58bc7db146f","tid":2192168,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"Chinese EV Startup Karma Accused of Stealing U.S. Rival&rsquo;s Plans<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-08-05/chinese-ev-startup-karma-accused-of-stealing-u-s-rival-s-plans\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-08-05%2Fchinese-ev-startup-karma-accused-of-stealing-u-s-rival-s-plans&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpyWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=b388afbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-08-05/chinese-ev-startup-karma-accused-of-stealing-u-s-rival-s-plans</a><br />\n<br />\nBy Gabrielle Coppola<br />\nAugust 6, 2020, 1:17 AM GMT+8<br />\n VLF says Karma CEO tried to usurp electric Humvee deal<br />\n Former GM executive Bob Lutz, Henrik Fisker Co-founded VLF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChinese electric-car startup Karma Automotive LLC is being accused of stealing vehicle plans from a U.S. company with which it discussed a joint venture.<br />\n<br />\nMichigan-based VLF Automotive, a niche carmaker co-founded by former General Motors Co. executive Bob Lutz, filed suit against Karma in California Superior Court in June. VLF claims it shared its plans for a &ldquo;luxury Humvee&rdquo; with Karma last fall as part of a proposed partnership to produce the vehicle for the Chinese market, only to have Karma try to cut it out of the deal.<br />\n<br />\nVLF is asking for at least $18.5 million in damages to cover its investment in the Humvee project and its share of the projected profits.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe lawsuit comes as Karma, which is owned by Chinese auto-parts maker Wanxiang Group, is trying to capitalize on the rally in shares of EV makers such as Tesla Inc. and Nikola Corp., a hydrogen trucking startup that went public as a blank-check company in June. Karma told Bloomberg in early July it had raised a third of the $300 million it&rsquo;s seeking by selling stakes to private equity investors.<br />\n<br />\nKarma Chief Strategy Officer Greg Tarr declined comment on the lawsuit. A lawyer for VLF also declined to comment......"},{"pid":"d300b7cc6b3119d10027adde53c825027bf308d0","tid":2192168,"uid":226466,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"Karma is a bitch<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47638d503ca801f739df7ac4a39516b6cca77cf1","tid":2192168,"uid":280648,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"karma呢個名改得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d69bd762b482d90f16de0834faa7252ed8023a","tid":2192168,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"is that karma?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f74c29ed7846b9389c90a4d97bf901f1c91ec2","tid":2192168,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴鳩線 1蚊入面有8毫4都係借番黎既話 呢間野到底點還錢"},{"pid":"b05f19dee0882e5c4e57e00166aaa09ab16cc142","tid":2192168,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7f74c29ed7846b9389c90a4d97bf901f1c91ec2","tid":2192168,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴鳩線 1蚊入面有8毫4都係借番黎既話 呢間野到底點還錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"樂視之前夠話設廠搞電動車啦<br />\n圈錢手段黎, 到咁上下就卷錢走人架喇"},{"pid":"bc09cdab5b3bfd2b3421c3ba4f2ea1459ecff8f2","tid":2192168,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7f74c29ed7846b9389c90a4d97bf901f1c91ec2","tid":2192168,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴鳩線 1蚊入面有8毫4都係借番黎既話 呢間野到底點還錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"班中國人借錢係唔打算還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.